This device is clearly manufactured by '''Askey'''. The test report seems to indicate that the device has a Ethernet WAN port, but the external photos for the device do not corroborate this.
This FCC ID also covers the 4112N. This device is used by '''AT&T'''.. and the default settings in this entry are for the '''AT&T''' branded unit. :Default SSID pattern: '''ATTXXX''', '''XXX''' appears to be the last 3 characters of the serial number (numeric only?)
